trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> class is a read-only collection of service principal names.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> é uma coleção somente leitura de nomes da entidade de serviço.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection> class is used in an <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ExtendedProtectionPolicy> when validating against a custom list of service provider names (SPNs).
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection> classe é usada em um <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ExtendedProtectionPolicy> durante a validação em relação a uma lista de nomes de provedor de serviço (SPNs) personalizados.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> class that contains the specified values of service names to be used to initialize the class.
trans-unit.target: Uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> que contém os valores especificados de nomes de serviço a serem usados para inicializar a classe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new read-only instance of the <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> class based on an existing <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância somente leitura da classe <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> com base em um <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> existente.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection> class that is initialized contains the specified values passed in the `items` parameter.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection> classe que é inicializado contém os valores especificados passados a `items` parâmetro.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="item" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="item" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="item" /> is empty.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="item" /> está vazio.

trans-unit.source: The string to seek.
trans-unit.target: A cadeia de caracteres a ser buscada.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the specified string occurs within this <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um valor que indica se a cadeia de caracteres especificada ocorre nesta instância de <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <paramref name="searchServiceName" /> parameter occurs within this <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o parâmetro <paramref name="searchServiceName" /> ocorre dentro desta instância de <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" />; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Merges the current <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> with the specified values to create a new <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> containing the union.
trans-unit.target: Mescla o <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> atual com os valores especificados para criar um novo <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> que contém a união.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerable" /> class that contains the specified values of service names to be merged.
trans-unit.target: Uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerable" /> que contém os valores especificados de nomes de serviço a serem mesclados.

trans-unit.source: Merges the current <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> with the specified values to create a new <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> containing the union.
trans-unit.target: Mescla o <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> atual com os valores especificados para criar um novo <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> que contém a união.

trans-unit.source: A new <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> instance that contains the union of the existing <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> instance merged with the specified values.
trans-unit.target: Uma nova instância de <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> que contém a união da instância de <see cref="T:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection" /> existente mesclada com os valores especificados.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection> class that is initialized contains the specified values passed in the `items` parameter.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection> classe que é inicializado contém os valores especificados passados a `items` parâmetro.

trans-unit.target: <paramref name="serviceNames" /> está vazio.

trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que contém os valores especificados de nomes de serviço a serem usados para inicializar a classe.

trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ServiceNameCollection> classe que é inicializado contém os valores especificados passados a `items` parâmetro.
